metadata.name: Vicugna Pacos #1
metadata.description: Story beging: In this busy world, people yearn for freedom and freedom of wealth. Pacos led his companions, breaking the existing worldview and embarking on a journey, fearless to complete the world people aspire to. Pacos has always believed that by relying on each other with his companions, he can continue to travel and find the new world he longs for.
